            <title><![CDATA[【#定期体检对预防肝癌非常重要#[话筒]】#乙肝患者如何避免发展成肝癌#？医生强调，定期体检非常重要。对于乙肝患者，尤其是已发生肝硬化者、有肝癌家族史者、长...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%B9%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E8%82%9D%E7%99%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F%E4%BD%93%E6%A3%80%E5%AF%B9%E9%A2%84%E9%98%B2%E8%82%9D%E7%99%8C%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8D%E8%A6%81%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#定期体检对预防肝癌非常重要#</span></a><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B9%99%E8%82%9D%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%88%90%E8%82%9D%E7%99%8C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B9%99%E8%82%9D%E6%82%A3%E8%80%85%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D%E5%8F%91%E5%B1%95%E6%88%90%E8%82%9D%E7%99%8C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#乙肝患者如何避免发展成肝癌#</span></a>？医生强调，定期体检非常重要。对于乙肝患者，尤其是已发生肝硬化者、有肝癌家族史者、长期酗酒者，应至少3个月检查一次肝功能、甲胎蛋白和B超，做到早发现、早治疗👇🏻 <a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>  <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4928197503156260" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视一套的微博视频</span></a> <br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/78ad4dbbly1hgbosxauqej217k0oi49t.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/BZuzGdcUlx087l8Yn2k8010412013ynS0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;E