            <title><![CDATA[【阿卫活动预告！8月深圳医疗盛会华丽回归！速速报名[求饶][求饶][求饶]】8月份的深圳绝对大把人来，毕竟这个8月深圳好戏连台，比如全国大咖齐聚的医疗盛会——...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【阿卫活动预告！8月深圳医疗盛会华丽回归！速速报名<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[求饶]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a2qiurao-7ad34b9c84.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[求饶]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a2qiurao-7ad34b9c84.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="url-icon"><img alt="[求饶]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/fb_a2qiurao-7ad34b9c84.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>】8月份的深圳绝对大把人来，毕竟这个8月深圳好戏连台，比如全国大咖齐聚的医疗盛会——今年8月份，全国卫生行业的“最强大脑”将再次云集深圳，以“推进医院高质量发展”为主题，聚焦高水平医疗服务、高效能医院管理，展开一场头脑风暴。时隔三年，深圳医院大会华丽回归，阿卫这就来浅剧透一下<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[doge]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/d_doge-be7f768d78.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>想去现场感受吗？报名渠道戳戳戳👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E6%96%B0%E9%B2%9C%E4%BA%8B%E5%84%BF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫新鲜事儿#</span></a> <a href="https://weibo.cn/sinaurl?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmp.weixin.qq.com%2Fs%2F8rClzspC58Hxl8hk4x7JTw" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_web_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">8月来深圳，除了告五人的演唱会，还有这场医疗盛会</span></a><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgcr5z67grj20v985ekjl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgcr60bpt5j20v99n1qv5.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgcr60r0p8j20v90wcabw.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgcrac7t63j20zk20w4e0.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax3.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgcraq3qeij20xc6hz7wi.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgcrasunh9j20xc6c31ky.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgcranbe85j20xc5uax6p.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgcrauch02j20xc4byhdt.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br><img style="" src="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/large/a8bfee30gy1hgcravqj3yj20xc4qhkjl.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><br><br>]]></description>
